reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Replaced my broken sprayer on my 2015 RAM 1500. Perfect fit. Installed very easily and it sprays exactly like my original sprayer.......UPDATE: As others have said, after roughly 4-5 times of use, the insides of the sprayer blew out, leaving the sprayer as a gusher. Seems to be a common issues with this product. Luckily i did not use the other sprayer and replaced it again, but I don't expect it to last any longer than the first one.Update 1-1-2024.... second sprayer blew out as well after about the third time used. Terrible product.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It works but sprays very low.
reviews.reviewText: Does it fit, yes. Does it function, yes. Does it spray way to low, also yes. Will update after using for a few days to see if I just take them back off and use my original ones.Update - contacted the seller and due to the issues I have they are sending me a replacement set. Will update once they arrive and are tested.Update #2- replacement sprayers arrived and so far are working flawlessly. Customer service with this seller is top notch and will happily order from them again should I need to.
